Define a product implementation class with the necessary fields. Add [getter method][1] implementations as required by the interfaces. 

    class Milk implements PerishableProduct {
        // Member fields. 
        private UUID id;
        private LocalDate expirationDate ;
    
        // Constructor
        public Milk ( final UUID id , final LocalDate expirationDate ) {
            this.id = id ;
            this.expirationDate = expirationDate ;
        }
    
        // Implement the interfaces methods. 
        public UUID getId() { return this.id ; }  // Required by Product interface. 
        public LocalDate getExpirationDate() { return this.expirationDate ; }  // Required by PerishableProduct interface. 
    }

