You can define an `aws_api_gateway_stage` which depends on `aws_api_gateway_deployment`. There is [a known issue, at the time of writing](https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform/issues/6613), where the deployment doesn&#39;t re-trigger, which was the original cause of my _forbidden_ error.

To fix this and get the deployment to run everytime a change has been made, add to `aws_api_gateway_deployment`:

```
resource &quot;aws_api_gateway_deployment&quot; &quot;gateway-deployment&quot; {
  ...

  stage_description = &quot;Terraform hash ${md5(join(&quot;,&quot;, local.all_resources))}&quot;

